laboratory_examinations.findings: Phe level in the classic range at 1642 µmol/L

laboratory_examinations.findings: Patient found to be homozygous for a three-basepair in-frame deletion variant c.169_171del, p.Glu57del in the PAH gene, consistent with autosomal recessive PKU. No other clinically relevant variants identified.
